{
  "title": "Xtra Chewy Mexican Provola Elote",
  "description": "A floral and chewy Mexican dish featuring provola cheese, perfect for a monsoon evening, this plant-based-friendly elote is broiled to perfection.",
  "cuisine": "Mexican",
